reviews.text: The congee is ok, the noodles and milk tea are above average. However, the plain tea tastes like water and the price is pretty high.
Very high quality wanton noodle and excellent congee. It is expensive but worth the price.
I love the congee here! The atmosphere is quite rowdy and loud, not relaxing but it's very Hong Kong hustle bustle!
Awesome wan tun noodle noodles, all dim sum great, spacious and luminous, good service, would come back again, and again.

Been here numerous times. Food is consistant, customer service has gotten better in the last two years since the manager from the Elements location has joined this store. The soup base has a really nice fish and chinese ham flavor. The noodles has the nice chewy texture

result.name: Tasty Congee & Noodle Wantun Shop 正斗粥麵專家

reviews.text:
座位寬敞、餐點好吃不會踩到雷，但服務品質就一般般，加茶要等好久，結帳人員態度冷漠！
給你一顆星是希望你們好好改善！

非用餐時段：
座位寬敞舒適。
服務人員態度很好。
雲吞麵 好吃😋 湯底味道很不錯👍🏼
份量較少。
這裡有湯麵 ，粥品 ，還有炒河粉 和 點心 ，價錢偏高 ，味道中規中矩 。
食物質素可以，座位間隔疏落坐得舒服，而且店員有禮貌親切，會不時為客人加茶。本身新城市就沒什麼好吃的，想吃得清淡健康一點時會再來。
The congee is ok, the noodles and milk tea are above average. However, the plain tea tastes like water and the price is pretty high.
